---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import NavStill from "../components/Nav-still.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Sales consulting. Customer outreach. Software development - Night of the Living Dev"
>
  <NavStill />
  <main>
    <h1
      class="font-poppins font-bold text-violet-100 text-4xl md:text-7xl px-2 text-center my-12 !leading-tight"
    >
      Pricing
    </h1>
    <div
      class="grid grid-rows-3 md:grid-rows-none md:grid-cols-3 px-2 max-w-7xl m-auto gap-10"
    >
      <div class="border-2 gradient-border border-solid p-8">
        <h3 class="text-slate-200 font-poppins text-3xl text-center">
          Sales<br />consulting
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="text-violet-400 text-3xl font-bold font-poppins text-center my-4"
        >
          $125/hour
        </h4>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4 text-center">
          With over 12 years of experience in inside and outside sales, I've
          learned and perfected the optimal techniques and strategies to
          maximize conversion at each stage of the sales funnel. I will coach
          you and your team on how to optimize your sales process, including
          lead generation, cold calling, cold emailing, messaging, demoing,
          managing pipeline and closing techniques.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 gradient-border border-solid p-8">
        <h3 class="text-slate-200 font-poppins text-3xl text-center">
          Customer<br />outreach
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="text-violet-400 text-3xl font-bold font-poppins text-center my-4"
        >
          $49/hour
        </h4>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4 text-center">
          If you need to contact potential clients, customers or users for
          customer discovery or product demonstrations, we have a team of
          trained business development reps available 9am-5pm EST. We can
          perform outreach via cold calling, cold emailing and social media
          outreach. We can also consult with you about which channels are best
          for your business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 gradient-border border-solid p-8">
        <h3 class="text-slate-200 font-poppins text-3xl text-center">
          Software<br />development
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="text-violet-400 text-3xl font-bold font-poppins text-center my-4"
        >
          $65/hour
        </h4>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4 text-center">
          I have 5+ years of experience developing software including web,
          mobile and blockchain applications. I've developed for solutions for
          everything from small startups to billion dollar enterprises. This
          service includes product roadmapping, testing and deployment of the
          application. It does not include any external fees such as web
          hosting.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadein 2s ease-in forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadein {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .gradient-border {
    background: linear-gradient(#181827 25%, #181827) padding-box,
      linear-gradient(to right, rgb(139, 92, 246), rgb(196, 181, 253))
        border-box;
    border-radius: 40px;
    border: 4px solid transparent;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
    a {
      margin: 16px 0px;
      padding: 0.2em 0;
    }
  }
  a {
    /* margin: 16px 0px; */
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    padding: 0.35em 0;
  }

  a.link::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 0.1em;
    background-color: rgb(142, 132, 249);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 300ms, transform 300ms;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(0);
    transform-origin: center;
  }

  a.link:hover::after {
    transform: scale(1);
  }

  .fromleft {
    animation: from-left 3s ease-in-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.25s;
  }
  .links-fade {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-in 3s forwards;
    animation-delay: 2.5s;
  }

  .logos-fade {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-in 3s forwards;
    animation-delay: 3.75s;
  }
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  .instructions {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 25%);
    background-color: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.4rem;
  }
  .instructions code {
    font-size: 0.875em;
    font-weight: bold;
    background: rgba(var(--accent), 12%);
    color: rgb(var(--accent));
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.3em 0.45em;
  }
  .instructions strong {
    color: rgb(var(--accent));
  }
  .link-card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  @keyframes fade-in {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes from-left {
    0% {
      margin-left: -100vw;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      margin-left: 0px;
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
